[30/05/2019 13:09:19] <font color="#ff00ff">De acuerdo.</font>
[30/05/2019 13:09:22] <font color="#ffff00">Lane.</font>
[30/05/2019 13:09:22] <font color="#00ffff">Dime.</font>
[30/05/2019 13:09:24] <font color="#ffff00">¿Esos salvajes iban pintados?</font>
